info.senderName: NWS Key West (Key West - The Florida Keys)
info.headline: Coastal Flood Statement issued November 03 at 3:55AM EDT until November 03 at 5:00PM EDT by NWS Key West
info.description: ...COASTAL FLOOD STATEMENT REMAINS IN EFFECT THROUGH LATE THIS AFTERNOON... * WHAT...Minor saltwater flooding. * WHERE...Middle Florida Keys. * WHEN...Through late this afternoon, especially at the time of high tide. * IMPACTS...Minor saltwater flooding of low elevation streets and lots is likely. Some storm drains will overflow, and some seawalls and docks will be overtopped. Boaters can expect less clearance under fixed bridges. Motorists should remember that persistent puddles around the times of high tide are almost certain to contain a mix of saltwater. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS...
info.instruction: Do not drive through flooded roadways.
